        <updateDate>2023-04-11T15:02:12Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Stop Trying to Obsessively Vilify Energy Act or the STOVE Act</b></p> <p>This bill prohibits federal agencies from promulgating rules or guidances that categorically restrict or ban the use and purchase of appliances powered by natural gas (e.g., cooktops, ranges, or ovens).</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
